  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Healthy 1 month infants exclusively formula-fed

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  gastrointestinal disorders (history of chronic diarrhoea or constipation,
             gastroesophageal reflux)

          -  gastrointestinal surgery

          -  cow's milk protein allergy

          -  metabolic disorders (diabetes, lactose intolerance)

          -  immune deficiency

          -  antibiotic prescription 1-week prior to inclusion and previous use of formula
             containing prebiotics or probiotics
      </textblock>
